        <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-blue-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0">▶</span><span><strong>GU (3 pts)</strong> — less known but valid, useful when U is hard to dump elsewhere</span></li>
      </ul>

